description:
&lt;p&gt;Newham Medical Centre is currently looking to appoint a full-time Reception Supervisor for our busy GP Practice. You will be responsible for the day to day supervision of the reception team and the associated functions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a friendly, innovative and supportive practice with a list size of 10150.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Clinical Team currently consists of 3 GP Partners, 3 Salaried GP’s, Nurse, HCA and Clinical Pharmacists. We are a training practice with medical students.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must also be flexible to cover holidays and sickness absence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary is negotiable and will be based on experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
